original_title: LAFFMOBB Presents Roz G: Ain't Got Jokes, Got Problems
overview: The brash New Jersey comedienne whose work as a substance abuse counselor and whose past struggles with addiction have led to a wealth of hilarious stories (such as helping prostitutes pad their resumes), takes the stage with her "evangelical" delivery style.
title: LAFFMOBB Presents Roz G: Ain't Got Jokes, Got Problems
